th permadeath for die-hard roguelike fans</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BEST PLAYED WITH</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/396750/extras/6a6d006020aaa466ad9974dad6edafc3.avif?t=1762910991\" width=360 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/396750/extras/4cae6f9883a2c9ff311e65731e1740f3.poster.avif?t=1762910991\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/396750/extras/4cae6f9883a2c9ff311e65731e1740f3.webm?t=1762910991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/396750/extras/4cae6f9883a2c9ff311e65731e1740f3.mp4?t=1762910991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
